      • getTableAsString

        public static java.lang.String getTableAsString(SQLiteDatabase db,
                                                java.lang.String tableName)
        Helper function that parses a given table into a string and returns it for easy printing. The string consists of the table name and then each row is iterated through with column_name: value pairs printed out.
        Parameters:
        db - the database to get the table from
        tableName - the the name of the table to parse
        Returns:
        the table tableName as a string
